<br>
So for OOW, why don't we push for a totally new song that boosts all melee-oriented stats (STR/STA/DEX/AGI).  Give it 60% haste  and +ATK like Mastruq.  Perhaps instead of a DS component, give it an +Endurance regen component.  We don't have any songs that buff all of the melee-oriented stats so IMO this would be a song to look forward to.  <br>
<br>
Safe to assume someone will say this is overpowering so for those who think that, offer an alternative with a similar concept that isn't a cookie cutter of a song we already have.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
<br>
